ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAppointment of RICK BEATON, Vice-President of Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation, of Sydney River, Nova Scotia, to be concurrently Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first, effective September 6, 2003.
